FOREWORD:
An unprofessional map created by me. This is actually my first real map, so i decided to "release" it (you gotta start with something anyway).

CONTENT:
Basically, this is a not too big bomb defuse map. Each side (T and CT) starts in a house, located on an open area, separated by a tall wall. They must both make their way to the bomb site first.

FEATURES:
This map has realistic lighting. It contain some static and moveable props, as well as breakable glass and ladders.

CREDITS:
All credit goes to me. I made this map on my own, and when i gain more experience in mapping, i will form a group to make bigger an better maps.

NOTE:
If you have any tips, comments,... feel free to tell me! You will help me in making better maps.
